@startuml
title Object lifecycle: Class Discord binding
[*] --> NotAssigned
NotAssigned --> Assigned : teacher assigns synced guild and channels
Assigned --> Assigned : notification/voice channels changed
Assigned --> Unassigned : teacher removes Discord guild
Assigned --> Stale : synced guild/channel no longer accessible
Stale --> Assigned : cache sync restores guild/channel
Stale --> Unassigned : teacher removes Discord guild
Unassigned --> [*]
@enduml
